Class UserToMemberMapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.neu.ccis.sms.entity.categories.UserToMemberMapping
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<UserToMemberMapping>

    @Entity
public class UserToMemberMapping
extends Object
implements Serializable, Comparable<UserToMemberMapping>
    Hibernate Entity bean class for UserToMemberMapping; Contain member to user mappings i.e. user is registered to which member and with which role, the registration status, time etc.
